==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Sureness
<hw>Sure"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state of being sure;
certainty.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>For more <qex>sureness</qex> he repeats it.</q>
<rj><qau>Woodward.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The law holds with equal <qex>sureness</qex> for all right
action.</q> <rj><qau>Emerson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Suresby</ent>⟦br⟧
